---
// 第二部分：角色介绍 - 双角色展示，半身立绘靠边站，文字居中错开
---
<section class="characters snap-section" id="characters">
  <div class="characters-inner">
    <!-- Rechor - 左侧立绘 -->
    <div class="char-portrait char-left">
      <img
        src="/Resources/Character_Rechor_1600x1600.png"
        alt="律可儿 Rechor"
        class="char-img"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- 中间文字区域 -->
    <div class="char-text-area">
      <!-- Rechor 文字 - 偏上 -->
      <div class="char-text char-text-top" style="--bright: #BCDE3C; --dark: #353638;">
        <h2 class="char-name" data-i18n="character.rechor.name">律可儿 Rechor</h2>
        <p class="char-desc" data-i18n="character.rechor.desc">
          来源不明的维修机器人，一直在里世界的实验室中负责日常维护。看似笨拙却总能交出能用的设备。胸口和腰间的微型显示屏时常闪烁着未知讯息。她似乎拥有超越礼貌的情感……但自己还没有意识到。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Eiria 文字 - 偏下 -->
      <div class="char-text char-text-bottom" style="--bright: #EED393; --dark: #2A2652;">
        <h2 class="char-name" data-i18n="character.eiria.name">小A Eiria</h2>
        <p class="char-desc" data-i18n="character.eiria.desc">
          大大咧咧的活力少女，真名 Eiria。在表世界遭到追杀时意外坠入里世界，发现了父亲留下的实验室。手持传家法杖，决心实施"细胞调律计划"，为人类的潜意识注入灵性。叛逆而坚毅，偶尔流露出大小姐气质。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Eiria - 右侧立绘 -->
    <div class="char-portrait char-right">
      <img
        src="/Resources/Character_Eiria_1600x1600.png"
        alt="小A Eiria"
        class="char-img"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .characters {
    position: relative;
    background: url('/Resources/bg_lab.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
    background-color: #0e1e30;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 0 4rem;
  }

  .characters-inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* 立绘容器 - 靠边站 */
  .char-portrait {
    position: relative;
    width: 25vw;
    max-width: 350px;
    min-width: 200px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .char-left {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .char-right {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .char-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 80vh;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
    /* 渐变淡出 - 上半身清晰，底部柔和融入背景 */
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 0%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 60%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 80%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%
    );
    mask-image: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 0%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 60%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 80%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%
    );
  }

  /* 中间文字区域 */
  .char-text-area {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .char-text {
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .char-text-top {
    align-self: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .char-text-bottom {
    align-self: flex-end;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* 主题色描边文字 */
  .char-name {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bright);
    text-shadow:
      -2px -2px 0 var(--dark),
      2px -2px 0 var(--dark),
      -2px 2px 0 var(--dark),
      2px 2px 0 var(--dark),
      0 0 12px var(--dark),
      0 0 24px var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .char-desc {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  /* 移动端适配：竖向堆叠 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .characters-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .char-portrait {
      width: 200px;
      min-width: unset;
    }

    .char-img {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .char-text-area {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .char-text {
      max-width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      align-self: center;
    }

    .char-text-top,
    .char-text-bottom {
      text-align: center;
      align-self: center;
    }
  }
</style>
